title: Tech closes out NCAA Indoor meet - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Tech closes out NCAA Indoor meet - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: BIRMINGHAM, Ala. – The Texas Tech track and field team wrapped up the NCAA Indoor championships Saturday night at the Birmingham CrossPlex. The TTU women scored 17 points, finishing 11th while the men scored 15 points to finish 17th.
